● Same pattern as the USING fixes — subject_key exists in both CTEs so the bare name in ORDER BY is ambiguous. One-line fix:

● Update(sql\queries\forecast_entries.sql)
  ⎿  Added 1 line, removed 1 line
      342     OR a.classification_id IS DISTINCT FROM b.classification_id
      343     OR a.employee_group_id IS DISTINCT FROM b.employee_group_id
      344     OR a.fte               IS DISTINCT FROM b.fte
